WITH unique_users AS
(
       SELECT u.uuid ,
              u.id AS user_id ,
              u.email ,
              CASE
                     WHEN u.display_name IS NOT NULL THEN u.display_name
                     ELSE CONCAT(u.first_name,' ',u.last_name)
              END AS user_name
       FROM   users u
       JOIN   user_attributions ua
       ON     ua.user_id = u.id
       WHERE  1=1
       AND    u.status = 'active'
       AND    ((
                            ua.KEY = 'current-country'
                     AND    ua.value = 'ID'
                     AND    u.dob > '1900-01-01')
              OR     (
                            ua.KEY = 'signup-country'
                     AND    ua.value = 'ID'
                     AND    u.dob > '1900-01-01'))
       OR     u.phone_country_code IN ('+62') ) , approved_listings AS
(
          SELECT    l.id              AS listing_id ,
                    l.registration_no AS plate_no ,
                    l.url ,
                    l.user_id AS host_id
          FROM      listings l
          LEFT JOIN listing_location ll
          ON        ll.listing_id = l.id
          WHERE     1=1
          AND       l.status   IN ('approved')
          AND       ll.country IN ('Indonesia')
          AND       l.deleted_at IS NULL ) , all_bookings AS
(
                SELECT DISTINCT
                ON (
                                                b.id) -- Booking Details
                                b.id AS booking_id ,
                                b.listing_id ,
                                l.host_id ,
                                u.uuid ,
                                u.user_name ,
                                u.email ,
                                l.plate_no ,
                                l.url ,
                                cc.NAME  AS plan_name ,
                                b.ref_no AS booking_ref ,
                                CASE
                                                WHEN b.reason ~~* '%test%' THEN 'test'
                                                WHEN b.status  IN ('cancelled',
                                                                   'withdrawn')
                                                AND             (
                                                                                b.reason ~~* '%host%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%kunci%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%available%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%bisa%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%tidak datang%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%pemilik%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%late%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%mobil tidak%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%tersedia%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%ready%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%full%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%never%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%rental%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%owner%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%belum%kabar%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%belum%tersedia%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%biaya%tambahan%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%host%tidak%hubungi%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%host%tidak%respon%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%mobil%kosong%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%mobil%tidak%ada%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%tambahan%biaya%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%tdk%tersedia%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%tidak%operasi%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%tidak%respon'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%tidak%tersedia%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%uang%tambahan%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%cancel'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%full%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%respond%' ) THEN 'rejected'
                                                WHEN b.status IN ('rejected')
                                                AND             (
                                                                                b.reason ~~* '%sim %'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%guest%'
                                                                OR              b.reason ~~* '%expired%' ) THEN 'withdrawn'
                                                ELSE b.status
                                END                                                                 AS booking_status ,
                                b.created_at at time zone 'Asia/Jakarta'                            AS booking_request_ts ,
                                date_trunc('month', b.created_at at     time zone 'Asia/Jakarta')::date AS booking_request_month ,
                                date_trunc('week', b.created_at at      time zone 'Asia/Jakarta')::date AS booking_request_week ,
                                date_trunc('month', b.request_end_at at time zone 'Asia/Jakarta')::date AS booking_end_month ,
                                date_trunc('week', b.request_end_at at  time zone 'Asia/Jakarta')::date AS booking_end_week ,
                                ceil(extract(epoch FROM b.request_end_at - b.request_start_at)/86400)   AS booking_dur_days -- Booking Value
                                ,
                                bp.discount_amount AS discount,
                                COALESCE(
                                CASE
                                                WHEN cc.NAME='Shield 25' THEN 0.2*bp.discount_amount
                                                ELSE 0
                                END,0) AS host_deduction,
                                CASE
                                                WHEN hp.booking_id IS NULL THEN ceil(b.gross_amount*(100-cc.PERCENT)/100)
                                                ELSE hp.amount
                                END AS payout_amount
                FROM            bookings b
                LEFT JOIN       booking_common_promos bp
                ON              b.id=bp.booking_id
                LEFT JOIN       approved_listings l
                ON              l.listing_id = b.listing_id
                LEFT JOIN       unique_users u
                ON              u.user_id = l.host_id
                LEFT JOIN       listing_commission_class lc
                ON              lc.listing_id = b.listing_id
                LEFT JOIN       commission_class cc
                ON              cc.id = lc.commission_id
                LEFT JOIN       payouts hp
                ON              hp.booking_id = b.id
                AND             hp.country ~* 'ID'
                WHERE           b.currency = 'idr') , bookings_data AS
(
         SELECT   b.host_id ,
                  b.uuid ,
                  b.email ,
                  b.user_name ,
                  b.booking_end_week ,
                  b.listing_id ,
                  b.plate_no ,
                  b.url ,
                  b.plan_name ,
                  count(DISTINCT
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('accepted',
                                                     'completed',
                                                     'start_driving',
                                                     'waiting_for_inspection',
                                                     'return_car',
                                                     'cancelled',
                                                     'rejected',
                                                     'requested') THEN b.booking_id
                           ELSE NULL
                  END) AS received_booking ,
                  count(DISTINCT
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('accepted',
                                                     'completed',
                                                     'start_driving',
                                                     'waiting_for_inspection',
                                                     'return_car') THEN b.booking_id
                           ELSE NULL
                  END) AS fulfiled_booking ,
                  count(DISTINCT
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('completed',
                                                     'start_driving',
                                                     'waiting_for_inspection',
                                                     'return_car') THEN b.booking_id
                           ELSE NULL
                  END) AS completed_booking ,
                  sum(
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('completed',
                                                     'start_driving',
                                                     'waiting_for_inspection',
                                                     'return_car')
                           AND      b.discount IS NOT NULL THEN 1
                           ELSE 0
                  END) AS discounted_booking ,
                  to_char(COALESCE(sum(
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('completed',
                                                     'start_driving',
                                                     'waiting_for_inspection',
                                                     'return_car') THEN b.discount
                           ELSE 0
                  END),0),'fm999999999d') AS total_discount ,
                  count(DISTINCT
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('rejected') THEN b.booking_id
                           ELSE NULL
                  END) AS rejected_booking ,
                  to_char((count(DISTINCT
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('accepted',
                                                     'completed',
                                                     'start_driving',
                                                     'waiting_for_inspection',
                                                     'return_car') THEN b.booking_id
                           ELSE NULL
                  END)::decimal / NULLIF(count(DISTINCT
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('accepted',
                                                     'completed',
                                                     'start_driving',
                                                     'waiting_for_inspection',
                                                     'return_car',
                                                     'cancelled',
                                                     'rejected',
                                                     'requested') THEN b.booking_id
                           ELSE NULL
                  END),0)::decimal)*100,'fm990D00%') AS fr ,
                  sum(
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('completed',
                                                     'start_driving',
                                                     'waiting_for_inspection',
                                                     'return_car') THEN b.booking_dur_days
                           ELSE 0
                  END) AS booking_dur_days ,
                  to_char(sum(
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('accepted',
                                                     'completed',
                                                     'start_driving',
                                                     'waiting_for_inspection',
                                                     'return_car') THEN b.host_deduction
                           ELSE 0
                  END),'fm999999999d') AS host_deduction ,
                  to_char(COALESCE(sum(
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('accepted',
                                                     'completed',
                                                     'start_driving',
                                                     'waiting_for_inspection',
                                                     'return_car') THEN b.payout_amount - b.host_deduction
                           ELSE 0
                  END),0),'fm999999999d') AS est_payout ,
                  sum(
                  CASE
                           WHEN b.booking_status IN ('rejected') THEN b.payout_amount
                           ELSE 0
                  END) AS est_loss
         FROM     all_bookings b
         WHERE    booking_end_week = date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK')
         GROUP BY 1,
                  2,
                  3,
                  4,
                  5,
                  6,
                  7,
                  8,
                  9)
SELECT   concat(extract(day FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK')), ' ',
         CASE
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=1 THEN 'Januari'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=2 THEN 'Februari'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=3 THEN 'Maret'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=4 THEN 'April'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=5 THEN 'Mei'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=6 THEN 'Juni'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=7 THEN 'Juli'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=8 THEN 'Agustus'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=9 THEN 'September'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=10 THEN 'Oktober'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=11 THEN 'November'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE - interval '1 WEEK'))=12 THEN 'Desember'
                  ELSE ''
         END) AS weekstart,
                  concat(extract(day FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY'), ' ',
         CASE
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=1 THEN 'Januari'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=2 THEN 'Februari'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=3 THEN 'Maret'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=4 THEN 'April'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=5 THEN 'Mei'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=6 THEN 'Juni'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=7 THEN 'Juli'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=8 THEN 'Agustus'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=9 THEN 'September'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=10 THEN 'Oktober'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=11 THEN 'November'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')=12 THEN 'Desember'
                  ELSE ''
         END,' ', extract(year FROM date_trunc('week', CURRENT_DATE) - interval '1 DAY')) AS weekend,
                  concat(extract(day FROM CURRENT_DATE), ' ',
         CASE
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=1 THEN 'Januari'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=2 THEN 'Februari'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=3 THEN 'Maret'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=4 THEN 'April'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=5 THEN 'Mei'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=6 THEN 'Juni'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=7 THEN 'Juli'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=8 THEN 'Agustus'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=9 THEN 'September'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=10 THEN 'Oktober'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=11 THEN 'November'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE)=12 THEN 'Desember'
                  ELSE ''
         END) AS estweekstart,
                  concat(extract(day FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY'), ' ',
         CASE
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=1 THEN 'Januari'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=2 THEN 'Februari'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=3 THEN 'Maret'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=4 THEN 'April'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=5 THEN 'Mei'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=6 THEN 'Juni'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=7 THEN 'Juli'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=8 THEN 'Agustus'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=9 THEN 'September'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=10 THEN 'Oktober'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=11 THEN 'November'
                  WHEN extract(month FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')=12 THEN 'Desember'
                  ELSE ''
         END,' ', extract(year FROM CURRENT_DATE + interval '5 DAY')) AS estweekend,
         *
FROM     bookings_data
WHERE    1=1
AND      received_booking > 0
AND      host_id NOT IN ( -- Trevo Operated
                         93151,
                         280508,
                         951523, -- Non Car
                         353865,
                         478706,
                         451183,
                         1168033,
                         285505,
                         102,
                         2272516 )
         /*AND      host_id IN ( 126582,
848165,
1447243,
1215945,
98167,
90409,
291231,
329663,
379472,
832140,
1073731,
575968 )*/
ORDER BY 1,
         15 DESC
